General.Name: iShares Russell 2500 ETF
General.Description: The fund generally will invest at least 80% of its assets in the component securities of its underlying index and may invest up to 20% of its assets in certain futures, options and swap contracts, cash and cash equivalents. The underlying index measures the performance of the small- to mid-capitalization sector of the U.S. equity market, as defined by FTSE Russell.
